A list of design patterns that you used and why/how.
Please include the names of all classes involved in the implementation of the pattern.
You can also include reasons for not using certain design patterns.

1. Builder. the builder design pattern is used in to build a trade.
   The class is TradeBuilder, in the trade folder.
   To build a trade that requires a lot of information, so the builder is used.
   It stores the date and time of the trade, the location of the trade will make,
   and stores the trade is permanent or not.
   And last put them together.
   The state of the trade is set to be in progress when a new trade is made

2. Factory Method.
   The factory method is used to create different types of users.
   The class is UserFactory, in the user folder.
   create different types of users dependent on the permission group that the user in